{"id":1153,"date":"2021-07-21T14:31:45","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T14:31:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/?page_id=1153"},"modified":"2022-03-11T22:52:51","modified_gmt":"2022-03-11T22:52:51","slug":"pneumatosis-intestinalis","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/pneumatosis-intestinalis\/","title":{"rendered":"Pneumatosis Intestinalis"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1153\" class=\"elementor elementor-1153\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-237806f elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"237806f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24d83c2\" data-id=\"24d83c2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8178bf5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8178bf5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Small Intestine: Pneumatosis Intestinalis<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pneumatosis Intestinalis<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d471cd6 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d471cd6\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-38381af\" data-id=\"38381af\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24a0219 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"24a0219\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Pneumatosis Definitions<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Pneumatosis Intestinalis \u2013 Gas Within the Bowel Wall of Small &amp; Large Intestine<ul><li>Also Known as Pneumatosis Cystoides Intestinalis or Intramural Gas<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Gastric Pneumatosis \u2013 Gas Within the Wall of the Stomach<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Pathogenic Theories<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Pathogenesis Likely Multifactorial<\/li><li><em>Mechanical<\/em> \u2013 Gas Dissects into the Bowel Wall<\/li><li><em>Bacterial<\/em> \u2013 Gas Produced by Bacteria that Have Migrated into Submucosal Tissue<\/li><li><em>Biochemical<\/em> \u2013 Excessive Gas Produced by Bacteria within Lumen Increases Pressure &amp; Forces Gas into Submucosal Tissue<\/li><li><em>Pulmonary<\/em> \u2013 Gas Leakage Through Alveoli Travels into the Retroperitoneum &amp; Localizes within the Bowel Mesentery<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Causes\/Associations<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary\/Idiopathic (15%)<\/li><li>Secondary\/Pathologic (85%)<ul><li><strong>COPD \u2013 The Most Common Association<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Intestinal Ischemia<\/strong><\/li><li>Necrotizing Enterocolitis<\/li><li>Crohn\u2019s Disease<\/li><li>Cystic Fibrosis<\/li><li>Asthma<\/li><li>Infection<\/li><li>Immunodeficiency\/AIDS<\/li><li>Steroids<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Radiographic Findings<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Most Common Site: <strong>Jejunum<\/strong><\/li><li>Appearance: Gas (Liner or Cystic) within Mucosa, Submucosa or Subserosa<ul><li>Subserosa More Common in Small Intestine<\/li><li>Submucosa More Common in Large Intestine<\/li><li>*Linear vs Cystic Morphology is Not Predictive of Clinically Worrisome Pathology<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Associated Findings Suggestive of Ischemia:<ul><li><strong>Portal Venous Gas<\/strong> (Although 30% of Portal Venous Gas is Idiopathic)<\/li><li>Decreased Mural Contrast-Enhancement<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Clinical Correlation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Most Are Clinically ASx<\/li><li>Complications:<ul><li>Obstruction<\/li><li>Intussusception<\/li><li>Ulceration &amp; GI Bleed<\/li><li>Pneumoperitoneum from Rupture of Subserosa Cysts<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Management Based on Etiology &amp; Presentation<\/li><li>Severity:<ul><li>60% Have Benign Disease<\/li><li>40% Have Pathologic Disease Requiring Surgical Intervention<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Strongest Predictor of Pathologic Cause Requiring Surgery: <strong>Lactate &gt; 2.0 mg\/dL<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f2800dd\" data-id=\"f2800dd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fad6665 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fad6665\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-7754 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Pneumatosis.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Pneumatosis.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Pneumatosis-300x215.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Pneumatosis Intestinalis<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec0b974 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ec0b974\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-7771 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Mesenteric-Gas.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Mesenteric-Gas.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Mesenteric-Gas-300x233.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Mesenteric Venous Gas<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5bdcaa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d5bdcaa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-7774 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Portal-Venous-Gas.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Portal-Venous-Gas.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Portal-Venous-Gas-300x241.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Portal Venous Gas<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<